#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:2
msgid "Tracing"
msgstr "跟踪"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:6
msgid ""
"``--enable-tracing`` **requires** ``--otlp-endpoint`` to be set. The "
"server will refuse to start if tracing is enabled without an OTLP "
"endpoint, since there is no local fallback for trace export."
msgstr "``--enable-tracing`` **要求** 设置 ``--otlp-endpoint``。如果启用追踪但没有 OTLP 端点，服务器将拒绝启动，因为没有本地回退用于追踪导出。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:10
msgid ""
"When tracing is enabled (``--enable-tracing --otlp-endpoint <URL>``), the"
" tracing subscriber creates OTel spans from START/END event pairs:"
msgstr "当启用追踪时（``--enable-tracing --otlp-endpoint <URL>``），追踪订阅者从 START/END 事件对创建 OTel spans："

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:13
msgid "``mp.store`` — from ``MP_STORE_START`` to ``MP_STORE_END``"
msgstr "``mp.store`` — 从 ``MP_STORE_START`` 到 ``MP_STORE_END``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:14
msgid "``mp.retrieve`` — from ``MP_RETRIEVE_START`` to ``MP_RETRIEVE_END``"
msgstr "``mp.retrieve`` — from ``MP_RETRIEVE_START`` to ``MP_RETRIEVE_END``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:15
msgid ""
"``mp.lookup_prefetch`` — from ``MP_LOOKUP_PREFETCH_START`` to "
"``MP_LOOKUP_PREFETCH_END``"
msgstr "``mp.lookup_prefetch`` — 从 ``MP_LOOKUP_PREFETCH_START`` 到 ``MP_LOOKUP_PREFETCH_END``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:17
msgid ""
"Each span carries event metadata as span attributes (e.g. ``device``, "
"``stored_count``, ``found_count``)."
msgstr "每个跨度携带事件元数据作为跨度属性（例如 ``device``、``stored_count``、``found_count``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:20
msgid ""
"View traces in any OTel-compatible backend such as **Jaeger** or "
"**Grafana Tempo**."
msgstr "在任何与 OTel 兼容的后端中查看追踪，例如 **Jaeger** 或 **Grafana Tempo**。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:36
msgid "Per-Request Hit-Rate Attributes"
msgstr "每个请求的命中率属性"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:38
msgid ""
"Each session is wrapped in a per-request root span — ``request`` for the "
"standard MP path and ``cb.request`` for the CacheBlend path — that nests "
"all child spans (``mp.store``, ``mp.retrieve``, ``mp.lookup_prefetch``) "
"beneath it.  When the lookup phase ends, the root span is annotated with "
"three OTel attributes that summarise the request-level cache hit rate:"
msgstr "每个会话都被包装在一个每请求根跨度中——标准 MP 路径的 ``request`` 和 CacheBlend 路径的 ``cb.request``——该根跨度将所有子跨度（``mp.store``、``mp.retrieve``、``mp.lookup_prefetch``）嵌套在其下。当查找阶段结束时，根跨度会被注释三个 OTel 属性，以总结请求级别的缓存命中率："

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:48
msgid "Attribute"
msgstr "属性"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:49
msgid "OTel type"
msgstr "OTel 类型"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:50
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:51
msgid "``hit_tokens``"
msgstr "``hit_tokens``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:52
#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:55
msgid "``int``"
msgstr "``int``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:53
msgid "Tokens served from L1+L2 (numerator)."
msgstr "从 L1+L2 提供的令牌（分子）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:54
msgid "``requested_tokens``"
msgstr "``requested_tokens``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:56
msgid "Chunk-aligned tokens submitted for lookup (denominator)."
msgstr "提交用于查找的块对齐令牌（分母）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:57
msgid "``hit_rate``"
msgstr "``hit_rate``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:58
msgid "``float``"
msgstr "``float``"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:59
msgid ""
"``hit_tokens / requested_tokens``; ``0.0`` when the denominator is zero."
"  Stored as a precomputed float because trace UIs (Tempo, Jaeger) cannot "
"derive it from two integer attributes at query time."
msgstr "``hit_tokens / requested_tokens``；当分母为零时为``0.0``。存储为预计算的浮点数，因为跟踪 UI（Tempo，Jaeger）无法在查询时从两个整数属性推导出它。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:63
msgid ""
"The attributes are written when ``MP_LOOKUP_PREFETCH_END`` (standard MP "
"path) or ``CB_LOOKUP_END`` (CacheBlend path) is processed — while the "
"root span is still open.  **Store-only requests** that never call "
"``lookup_prefetch_start()`` emit no end event for the lookup phase, so "
"their root span will not carry these attributes."
msgstr "在处理 ``MP_LOOKUP_PREFETCH_END``（标准 MP 路径）或 ``CB_LOOKUP_END``（CacheBlend 路径）时，会写入这些属性——此时根跨度仍然是打开的。**仅存储请求**在未调用 ``lookup_prefetch_start()`` 时不会为查找阶段发出结束事件，因此它们的根跨度将不会携带这些属性。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:69
msgid "Example TraceQL queries (Grafana Tempo):"
msgstr "示例 TraceQL 查询（Grafana Tempo）："

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:82
msgid ""
"For the full event-to-span mapping and the registry pattern that links "
"child spans back to the root see ``docs/design/observability/request-"
"event-span.md`` in the source tree."
msgstr "有关完整的事件到跨度映射以及将子跨度链接回根的注册模式，请参阅源树中的 ``docs/design/observability/request-event-span.md``。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:89
msgid "Trace Recording"
msgstr "追踪记录"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:93
msgid ""
"Trace recording is **distinct from** ``--enable-tracing`` (OTel spans). "
"Trace recording captures every ``StorageManager`` public-API call to a "
"binary file so the same workload can be **replayed** later for testing, "
"regression hunting, and benchmarking — without needing vLLM and "
"(eventually) without a GPU. ``--enable-tracing`` exports live OTel spans "
"to an OTLP endpoint for online observability. The two features are "
"independent and can be used together."
msgstr "跟踪记录与 ``--enable-tracing``（OTel 跨度）是 **不同的**。跟踪记录捕获每个 ``StorageManager`` 公共 API 调用到一个二进制文件，以便可以在后续进行测试、回归排查和基准测试时 **重放** 相同的工作负载——无需 vLLM，并且最终无需 GPU。``--enable-tracing`` 将实时 OTel 跨度导出到 OTLP 端点以进行在线可观察性。这两个功能是独立的，可以一起使用。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:101
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"When ``--trace-level storage`` is set, LMCache records every call to "
"``StorageManager.{reserve_write, finish_write, submit_prefetch_task, "
"read_prefetched_results, finish_read_prefetched}`` to a binary file for "
"later replay."
msgstr "当设置 ``--trace-level storage`` 时，LMCache 会将每次对 ``StorageManager.{reserve_write, finish_write, submit_prefetch_task, read_prefetched_results, finish_read_prefetched}`` 的调用记录到一个二进制文件中，以便后续重放。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:106
msgid ""
"Recording is **off by default** and adds near-zero overhead when off (a "
"single boolean check per ``StorageManager`` call). When on, recording "
"happens on the EventBus drain thread, off the request path."
msgstr "记录默认是**关闭的**，关闭时几乎没有开销（每个``StorageManager``调用只需进行一次布尔检查）。开启时，记录发生在 EventBus 排水线程上，而不在请求路径上。"

