msgstr "回放记录的追踪，以及用于驱动、监控和导出回放结果的完整 CLI 标志集，已在其专门页面中介绍： :doc:`/mp/tracing_and_debugging`。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:143
msgid "What is captured (and what is not)"
msgstr "捕获了什么（以及未捕获的内容）"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:145
msgid "**Captured:**"
msgstr "**捕获：**"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:147
msgid "The fully-qualified name of every decorated ``StorageManager`` call."
msgstr "每个被装饰的 ``StorageManager`` 调用的完全限定名称。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:148
msgid ""
"Each call's input arguments (e.g. ``keys``, ``layout_desc``, ``mode``, "
"``extra_count``, ``external_request_id``)."
msgstr "每个调用的输入参数（例如 ``keys``, ``layout_desc``, ``mode``, ``extra_count``, ``external_request_id``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:150
msgid "Wall-clock and monotonic timestamps of each call."
msgstr "每个调用的墙钟时间和单调时间戳。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:151
msgid ""
"A header carrying a trace schema version, start times, and a SHA-256 "
"digest of the active ``StorageManagerConfig`` so replay can detect "
"mismatched configurations."
msgstr "一个包含跟踪模式版本、开始时间和活动的 ``StorageManagerConfig`` 的 SHA-256 摘要的头，以便重放可以检测到不匹配的配置。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:155
msgid "**Not captured:**"
msgstr "**未捕获：**"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:157
msgid ""
"KV tensor bytes. Replay exercises bookkeeping and controller logic; "
"payloads at replay time are zeros."
msgstr "KV 张量字节。重放练习的簿记和控制逻辑；重放时的有效负载为零。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:159
msgid ""
"Calls inside the ``MPCacheServer``, the message queue, or any GPU-copy "
"code. These layers are **out of scope** for the storage trace level."
msgstr "在 ``MPCacheServer``、消息队列或任何 GPU 复制代码中的调用。这些层是 **超出存储跟踪级别的范围**。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:164
msgid "File format"
msgstr "文件格式"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:166
msgid "A length-prefixed `msgpack <https://msgpack.org/>`_ stream:"
msgstr "一个长度前缀的 `msgpack <https://msgpack.org/>`_ 流："

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:175
msgid ""
"The ``Header`` carries a magic prefix (``LMCT``), a format version, the "
"trace level (``storage`` today), a trace schema version, start "
"timestamps, and the StorageManagerConfig digest. Each ``Record`` carries "
"a relative timestamp, a wall-clock timestamp, the fully-qualified call "
"site (``qualname``), and an argument dict."
msgstr "``Header`` 包含一个魔术前缀 (``LMCT``)、一个格式版本、跟踪级别 (今天是 ``storage``)、一个跟踪模式版本、开始时间戳和 StorageManagerConfig 摘要。每个 ``Record`` 包含一个相对时间戳、一个墙钟时间戳、完全限定的调用位置 (``qualname``) 和一个参数字典。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:181
msgid ""
"The format is deliberately extensible: future trace **levels** (``mq``, "
"``gpu``) will share this layout and use the ``level`` header field to "
"discriminate. Additional captured ops add new ``qualname`` strings "
"without bumping the format version."
msgstr "该格式故意具有可扩展性：未来的追踪 **级别** (``mq``, ``gpu``) 将共享此布局，并使用 ``level`` 头字段进行区分。额外捕获的操作会添加新的 ``qualname`` 字符串，而不会提升格式版本。"

#: ../../source/mp/observability/traces.rst:186
msgid "For the full design rationale see"
msgstr "有关完整的设计原理，请参见"

